## ğŸ“ File & Directory Commands

| Command | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| `ls` | List files |
| `ls -a` | Show hidden files |
| `pwd` | Current directory |
| `cd folder` | Enter folder |
| `cd ..` | Go back |
| `mkdir folder` | Create folder |
| `rmdir folder` | Remove empty folder |
| `rm file.txt` | Delete file |
| `rm -rf folder` | Delete folder |
| `cp a.txt b.txt` | Copy file |
| `cp -r dir1 dir2` | Copy folder |
| `mv a.txt dir/` | Move file |
| `mv old new` | Rename |
| `tree` | Folder tree |
| `touch file.txt` | Create file |

---

## ğŸ“„ File Viewing & Editing

| Command | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| `cat file.txt` | Show content |
| `less file.txt` | Read page |
| `head file.txt` | First lines |
| `tail file.txt` | Last lines |
| `nano file.txt` | Edit file |
| `vim file.txt` | Advanced editor |
| `clear` | Clear terminal |
| `history` | Command history |

