## ğŸ” Search & Find

| Command | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| `find / -name file` | Find file |
| `locate file` | Quick search |
| `grep "text" file` | Search text |
| `grep -r "text" .` | Search folder |
| `which python` | Path |
| `whereis git` | Binary location |

