## ğŸ“¦ Package Management (APT)

| Command | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| `sudo apt update` | Update repo |
| `sudo apt upgrade` | Upgrade |
| `sudo apt install git` | Install |
| `sudo apt remove git` | Remove |
| `dpkg -l` | List packages |

