## ğŸ–¥ System Info

| Command | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| `uname -a` | Kernel info |
| `hostname` | PC name |
| `uptime` | Running time |
| `top` | Running processes |
| `htop` | Better top |
| `free -h` | RAM |
| `df -h` | Disk |
| `du -sh folder` | Folder size |
| `whoami` | Current user |
| `id` | User ID |

