## ğŸŒ Networking

| Command | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| `ip a` | IP address |
| `ping google.com` | Check net |
| `traceroute google.com` | Trace |
| `netstat -tuln` | Ports |
| `ss -tuln` | Modern netstat |
| `curl url` | Fetch data |
| `wget url` | Download |
| `ifconfig` | Old IP |
| `nmcli` | Network manager |

